---
import SiteFooter from "../components/SiteFooter.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Meet Kai Liu, a TEDx speaker, communication coach, speech and debate trainer, and award-winning Toastmasters leader."
    />
    <title>About Coach Kai | SpeakKai</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        font-family:
          Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
          "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background: #f5f7fa;
        color: #071b3d;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html,
      body {
        min-height: 100%;
        margin: 0;
      }

      body {
        background: #f5f7fa;
      }

      main {
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .coach-banner {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 4 / 1;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: #020b20;
      }

      .coach-banner picture,
      .coach-banner img {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
      }

      .coach-banner img {
        object-fit: contain;
      }

      .site-header {
        display: flex;
        min-height: 48px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #d5deed;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .site-nav {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: clamp(22px, 4vw, 52px);
      }

      .site-nav a {
        padding: 14px 4px 12px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
        color: #294568;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .site-nav a:hover,
      .site-nav a[aria-current="page"] {
        border-bottom-color: #19a9c5;
        color: #0a5f91;
      }

      .site-nav a:focus-visible {
        border-radius: 3px;
        outline: 3px solid #80d6d1;
        outline-offset: 2px;
      }

      .about-section,
      .leadership-section,
      .coaching-section {
        scroll-margin-top: 56px;
      }

      .about-section {
        padding: clamp(58px, 8vw, 96px) 0;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .about-inner,
      .section-inner {
        width: min(100% - 40px, 1120px);
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .about-intro {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.45fr) minmax(280px, 0.75fr);
        align-items: start;
        gap: clamp(42px, 7vw, 88px);
      }

      .section-kicker {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        color: #087c98;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 900;
        line-height: 1.2;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .about-copy h1,
      .section-heading h2 {
        margin: 0;
        color: #10284d;
        letter-spacing: 0;
      }

      .about-copy h1 {
        font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 72px);
        line-height: 0.98;
      }

      .about-role {
        margin: 18px 0 0;
        color: #0a5f91;
        font-size: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 25px);
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.35;
      }

      .about-story {
        max-width: 760px;
        margin: 26px 0 0;
        color: #42546b;
        font-size: 17px;
        line-height: 1.75;
      }

      .about-metrics {
        display: grid;
        gap: 0;
        margin: 2px 0 0;
        border-top: 1px solid #cbd7e7;
      }

      .about-metrics div {
        display: grid;
        gap: 4px;
        padding: 19px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #cbd7e7;
      }

      .about-metrics dt {
        color: #0b5fc7;
        font-size: 30px;
        font-weight: 900;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .about-metrics dd {
        margin: 0;
        color: #52647b;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      .career-path {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
        margin-top: clamp(48px, 7vw, 76px);
        border-top: 1px solid #b9c9dd;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #b9c9dd;
      }

      .career-step {
        padding: 24px 22px 26px 0;
      }

      .career-step + .career-step {
        padding-left: 22px;
        border-left: 1px solid #b9c9dd;
      }

      .career-year {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        color: #087c98;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 900;
      }

      .career-step strong {
        display: block;
        color: #18345d;
        font-size: 17px;
        line-height: 1.35;
      }

      .career-step p {
        margin: 8px 0 0;
        color: #607087;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .leadership-section {
        padding: clamp(58px, 8vw, 90px) 0;
        border-top: 1px solid #d3deec;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #d3deec;
        background: #eef4fb;
      }

      .section-heading {
        max-width: 760px;
      }

      .section-heading h2 {
        font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 48px);
        line-height: 1.08;
      }

      .section-heading > p:last-child {
        margin: 16px 0 0;
        color: #586a81;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .leadership-layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(280px, 0.8fr) minmax(0, 1.2fr);
        gap: clamp(44px, 7vw, 82px);
        margin-top: 42px;
      }

      .credential-list,
      .outcome-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 0;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #b8c8dc;
      }

      .credential-list li,
      .outcome-list li {
        padding: 17px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #b8c8dc;
        color: #324a69;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .credential-list strong,
      .outcome-list strong {
        color: #102c54;
      }

      .achievement-list {
        display: grid;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #9fb3cb;
      }

      .achievement-list li {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 72px minmax(0, 1fr);
        gap: 20px;
        padding: 15px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #b8c8dc;
      }

      .achievement-list time {
        color: #0b68bb;
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 900;
      }

      .achievement-list span {
        color: #324a69;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .coaching-section {
        padding: clamp(58px, 8vw, 90px) 0;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .coaching-columns {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: clamp(28px, 4vw, 52px);
        margin-top: 42px;
      }

      .coaching-column {
        min-width: 0;
      }

      .coaching-column + .coaching-column {
        padding-left: clamp(28px, 4vw, 52px);
        border-left: 1px solid #cbd7e7;
      }

      .coaching-column h3 {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        color: #17345e;
        font-size: 21px;
        line-height: 1.25;
      }

      .coaching-column p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #52647b;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .coaching-column p + p {
        margin-top: 14px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .coach-banner {
          aspect-ratio: 1683 / 935;
        }

        .site-header {
          min-height: 46px;
        }

        .site-nav {
          width: 100%;
          gap: 0;
        }

        .site-nav a {
          flex: 1 1 16.666%;
          padding: 13px 2px 11px;
          font-size: clamp(10px, 3.2vw, 13px);
          text-align: center;
        }

        .about-inner,
        .section-inner {
          width: min(100% - 32px, 540px);
        }

        .about-intro,
        .leadership-layout,
        .coaching-columns {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .about-intro { gap: 36px; }
        .about-story { font-size: 16px; }

        .career-path {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          margin-top: 44px;
        }

        .career-step,
        .career-step + .career-step {
          padding: 20px 0;
          border-left: 0;
        }

        .career-step + .career-step {
          border-top: 1px solid #b9c9dd;
        }

        .leadership-layout,
        .coaching-columns { gap: 36px; }

        .achievement-list li {
          grid-template-columns: 58px minmax(0, 1fr);
          gap: 12px;
        }

        .coaching-column + .coaching-column {
          padding-top: 30px;
          padding-left: 0;
          border-top: 1px solid #cbd7e7;
          border-left: 0;
        }

      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="coach-banner" aria-label="Coach Kai">
        <picture>
          <source
            media="(max-width: 640px)"
            srcset="/images/coach-kai-banner-mobile.png"
          />
          <img
            src="/images/coach-kai-banner-desktop.png"
            width="2508"
            height="627"
            alt="Coach Kai"
          />
        </picture>
      </section>

      <header class="site-header">
        <nav class="site-nav" aria-label="Main navigation">
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <a href="/about/" aria-current="page">About</a>
          <a href="/schedule/">Schedule</a>
          <a href="/tools/">Tools</a>
          <a href="/resources/">Resources</a>
          <a href="/contact/">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="about-section" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-title">
        <div class="about-inner">
          <div class="about-intro">
            <div class="about-copy">
              <p class="section-kicker">About Coach Kai</p>
              <h1 id="about-title">Kai Liu</h1>
              <p class="about-role">
                TEDx Speaker | Communication Coach | Speech &amp; Debate Coach
              </p>
              <p class="about-story">
                A first-generation Chinese American, Kai built his career by
                confronting the same challenges he now helps others overcome:
                a stutter, fear of public speaking, and difficulty expressing
                ideas with confidence. Teaching English while learning Mandarin
                in China helped him find his voice. His work grew from language
                training and education consulting into competitive speech,
                debate, storytelling, and leadership development for students
                and professionals.
              </p>
            </div>

            <dl class="about-metrics" aria-label="Career highlights">
              <div>
                <dt>15+ years</dt>
                <dd>Education and communication training</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt>1,000+</dt>
                <dd>Presentations delivered across seven countries</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt>2,000+</dt>
                <dd>Students trained in speaking, debate, and confidence</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>

          <div class="career-path" aria-label="Career path">
            <article class="career-step">
              <span class="career-year">2007-2012</span>
              <strong>English Trainer</strong>
              <p>Adapted communication curricula for learners from children to professionals.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="career-step">
              <span class="career-year">2012-2015</span>
              <strong>Education Consultant</strong>
              <p>Built university strategies and coached high-stakes international interviews.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="career-step">
              <span class="career-year">2015-2017</span>
              <strong>Test Preparation</strong>
              <p>Taught structured argument, writing, and speaking for IELTS, TOEFL, and SAT.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="career-step">
              <span class="career-year">2017-Present</span>
              <strong>Speech &amp; Debate Coach</strong>
              <p>Develops speakers, debate teams, TEDx talks, and professional presentations.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="leadership-section" aria-labelledby="leadership-title">
        <div class="section-inner">
          <header class="section-heading">
            <p class="section-kicker">Toastmasters</p>
            <h2 id="leadership-title">Leadership and competition</h2>
            <p>
              Nine years of continuous Toastmasters leadership, extensive club
              service, and a District 85 competition record across evaluation,
              Table Topics, and International Speech.
            </p>
          </header>

          <div class="leadership-layout">
            <ul class="credential-list" aria-label="Toastmasters leadership credentials">
              <li><strong>Past President</strong> of Shanghai No.1, Xujiahui, Imagine, and Teachers Bilingual Toastmasters clubs.</li>
              <li><strong>Division N Director, District 85 (2019-2020)</strong>, leading 20 clubs and approximately 500 members.</li>
              <li>Organized two Club Officer Training programs for <strong>120 participants each</strong>.</li>
              <li>Completed <strong>six Toastmasters Pathways</strong> and the Competent Communicator manual.</li>
              <li>District trainer and public-relations sharing speaker across Districts 85, 88, 89, 118, and 128.</li>
            </ul>

            <ol class="achievement-list" aria-label="Selected Toastmasters competition results">
              <li><time>2018</time><span>District 85 Area 02 Table Topics Champion</span></li>
              <li><time>2019</time><span>District 85 Division Evaluation Contest Finalist</span></li>
              <li><time>2021</time><span>District 85 Evaluation Runner-up and International Speech Finalist</span></li>
              <li><time>2022</time><span>District 85 Table Topics Second Runner-up and International Speech Second Runner-up</span></li>
              <li><time>2024</time><span>District 85 Table Topics Finalist and Train-the-Trainer program trainer</span></li>
              <li><time>2025</time><span>District 85 Evaluation Finalist</span></li>
              <li><time>2026</time><span>District 85 Table Topics Finalist and International Speech Runner-up</span></li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="coaching-section" aria-labelledby="coaching-title">
        <div class="section-inner">
          <header class="section-heading">
            <p class="section-kicker">Coaching and training</p>
            <h2 id="coaching-title">From classrooms to global stages</h2>
            <p>
              Kai combines competitive speaking technique with critical
              thinking, storytelling, and practical performance coaching.
            </p>
          </header>

          <div class="coaching-columns">
            <article class="coaching-column">
              <h3>Student results</h3>
              <p>
                Coached national champions and finalists across HOSA, USAD,
                National History Day, ESDP, TOC, WSDA, and the World Forensics
                League in original oratory, expository speaking, storytelling,
                debate, hosting, writing, and interviews.
              </p>
              <p>
                He has also served as a judge for Toastmasters, USAD, HOSA,
                WSDA, and Star of Outlook competitions.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="coaching-column">
              <h3>Corporate communication</h3>
              <p>
                Delivered training in business storytelling, persuasion,
                customer service, investor pitching, presentation skills, and
                sales communication for Microsoft, Entegris, AIA, fintech
                teams, law firms, and creative companies.
              </p>
              <p>
                A TEDxSMIC speaker and TEDx coach, Kai has presented in New
                York, Singapore, Thailand, Vietnam, and cities across China.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="coaching-column">
              <h3>Global mentorship</h3>
              <p>
                His professional development includes programs created by
                World Champions Darren LaCroix, Mark Brown, and Craig Valentine,
                plus coaching from 2021 World Champion Verity Price and world
                finalists Kwong Yue Yang, Kin Ng, and Fursey Gotuaco.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>
    <SiteFooter />
  </body>
</html>
